Package com.att.aro.main.menu.view

Class Summary
ChartPlotOptionsDialog Represents the chart plot options dialog.
ExcludeTimeRangeAnalysisDialog Represents the Select Time Range Dialog Dialog (accessed through the View menu) that allows the user to set a time range that delineates a section of the trace data to be analyzed.
FilterApplicationsAndIpDialog Represents the Filter Applications Dialog that appears when the user chooses the Select Applications/IPs menu item under the View menu.
FilterProcessesDialog Represents the Select Processes options dialog.
